I have in general found nearly all mail order outlets to be dishonest in 
shipping schedule claims.  I work for UCLA which faxes them a PO with dire 
warnings about State audits, etc.  and three companies have weasled out of the 
contracts upon receiving the PO...feigning various problems, most of 
which were transparent.  Most mail order houses are really up to no good, and 
we need a consumer law to protect us.

